entries.title_d: More of the Imperial fleet have arrived to the Endor sector but instead of just trying to hide, we have decided to launch attacks on the Empire while they are not at full strength. Your task is to meet with one of Nym's smugglers that have brought highly valuable intel data from the Lok Alliance Navy on the Imperial fleet moving this way.
entries.title: Endor system: Bring Intel data to Fleet Command.
entries.split_quest_alert: Rebel Fleet Command: < We have the confirmed location of one of the Empires advanced spy ships and need you to take him out, proceed. >
entries.quest_rendezvous2_t: Bring data to Rebel command ship.
entries.quest_rendezvous2_d: Bring the data to our command ship at these coordinates. Be careful, the Imperial presence in this system is increasing more and more.
entries.quest_rendezvous1_d: The Nym smuggler has provided you with coordinates to meet up with him. Hurry over there and get that data.
entries.quest_location_d: We have managed to gather more information on the Endor system and unfortunately it seems to be quite crowded with Imperial forces (and more on the way). We are not sure why at this point as the information we have on the forest moon of Endor doesn't suggest any value.
entries.quest_dock2_d: Dock with our command ship and transfer the data quickly before more of the Imperial menace shows up.
entries.quest_dock1_d: Dock with the Nym smuggler so that he can transfer over the Intel data about the Imperial fleet to your ship.
entries.hello_p: Hey Rebel, I've got your goods. Lets dock so I can transfer this and be out of here.
entries.hello_d: This is Rebel Command ship Starsurfer, initiating docking sequence.
entries.found_loc_p: Meet the smuggler at these coordinates, good luck!
entries.found_loc_d: Meet the HQ ship at this location. There's a lot of Imperials in your area, we're counting on you to be able to take care of them.
entries.failed_destroyed: How could you let this happen pilot? Return to base immediately!
entries.docking_started_delivery: Downloading data, this will only take a few seconds pilot.
entries.docking_complete_pickup: There ya go, my end of the deal is over. Be careful, there's Imps all over this sector.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Alright we got it. Good work pilot. We have another task that need your immediate attention.
entries.attack_stopped: Tactical Computer: < No more fighter vessels within sensor range. >
entries.attack_notify: Tactical Computer: < Incoming fighter vessels. Scans show weapons armed. >
entries.arrived_at_pickup: Dock with the Nym smuggler and pick up the data.
entries.arrived_at_delivery: Excellent, prepare to dock and transfer the data.
